Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,幹麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因為已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這次的主題知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,穿這樣也可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你還沒準備好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這也難怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你不知道企劃對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:01:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這次的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是以粉絲為主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,首先呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,先讀一下企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你的腦粉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我好希望說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可以跟你像情侣一樣度过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,假如有這種企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,請一定要讓我參加
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:02:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真热情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有點驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,還有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,當然很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣支持我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好熱烈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,想回饋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:03:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以讓你去訪問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,當然就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,獨處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你跟他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一開始我會在啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子的企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:04:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就出發囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,笑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一下不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,加油就對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:05:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&Hffffff\c&Hff&\fn楷体\b1\fs16}《与日向真凛完全二人独处的住宿粉丝感谢企划射精\N次数全8次！和憧憬的女演员一起度过一晚两天一夜的感谢特别篇》\N{\3c&H00\c&Hffffff&\fn楷体\fs12\b1}（日向真凛)\N{\fntimes new roman\fs8\b1}SSNI-933\N{\c&H3ee0fd&\fs8\fn宋体}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,現在有好多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,還在緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你會不安嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,多少啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:06:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,看過這種企劃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,自己沒玩過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真的有點緊張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哈囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,起來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,睡成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,現在下大雨喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:07:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是看不清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊要這樣拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有點擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不過沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,啥都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,時間會延後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,終於看的清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,雨變小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,時間還是延後不少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好誇張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊今天的雨量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:09:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,還是在下雨啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,能小就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,現在好多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我開始想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,對方的年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,會介意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,應該說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,年紀不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,對應方式也不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:10:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是還是要做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,當然要做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你的意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不同的切入法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我會擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,擔心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,到了就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:11:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好了要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊張喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,往前面走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊張喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不用緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜點喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:12:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你跟粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,獨處時間囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,準備真充分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,按電鈴對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:13:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微進去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因為雨很大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,MIUR\N不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,先打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是進來做點作業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:14:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你想跟他獨處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊我好愛她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不過想怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,情侶的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:15:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,濃情蜜意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他這樣說喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,試著想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,情境吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你會離開喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:16:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我要準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你也準備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你看什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,照片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,喔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:17:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,想像你能穿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己整理的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好了差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你是結婚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:18:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這跟女神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是不同的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不同的驚戒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,交往很久的樣子』
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好強喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要跟他好好過活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要發洩一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你的妄想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:19:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他講得很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你接受到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,時間上有點趕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,今天最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,最後的瘋狂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:20:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
